<h1>Test adding a new tag (using API)</h1>
<p>Test the POST method of the API. Add a new tag name and press submit! If everything is OK, you should see the new tag created on <a href="http://dev.doxsite.com/tags">dev.doxsite.com/tags</a> .</p>
<p>You can also see list of all tag id's <%= link_to "here", tags_all_path %> .</p>
<%= form_tag  do %>
  <div class="field">
    <%= label_tag("New Tag") %>
    <%= text_field_tag(:tag_name) %>
  </div>

  <div class="actions">
    <%= submit_tag("Add New Tag") %>
  </div>
<% end %>

